title: 299 - The Wrong Tribe
description:
Do you mismanage what has been given to you or do you take your time and money and give it to individuals that are not good stewards of what has been given to them? In this episode, the guys share candidly that in order to get to the next level of success, you have to be willing to do some things differently. You can’t get anywhere new if you don’t do something new and sometimes that means divorcing yourself from things and people that are holding you back. 

Listener Perks

INDEED specializes in finding and pairing your business with the best qualified candidates. More than 73% of online job seekers visit INDEED weekly and over 90% of employers get qualified candidates when they sponsor their job posts. For a $75 credit to sponsor your first job go to www.indeed.com/success.
